  "page": "Nicol",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/50px-Maester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/75px-Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/100px-Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Maester</span><br />Nicol</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/50px-Maester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/75px-Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/100px-Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">The Citadel</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Nicol</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\">maester</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a> who wrote the book <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Measure_of_the_Days\" title=\"The Measure of the Days\">The Measure of the Days</a></i> in which he argued that <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros#Known_seasons\" title=\"Westeros\">seasons</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">world</a> might once have been of <a href=\"/index.php/Measurement\" title=\"Measurement\">regular length</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_long_night.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_long_night.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nicol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Nicol and his <i>Measure of the Days</i> is a reference to <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nicolaus_Copernicus\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Nicolaus Copernicus\">Nicolaus Copernicus</a> and his <i><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/De_revolutionibus_orbium_coelestium\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:De revolutionibus orbium coelestium\">On the Revolutions of the Heavenly Spheres</a></i>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nicol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_long_night.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_long_night.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Ancient History: The Long Night.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403143520\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.065 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.253 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 411/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10396/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4898/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 401/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 652/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.46 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  244.702      1 -total\n 97.80%  239.325      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 97.04%  237.467      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.45%   28.029     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  5.32%   13.021      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.60%    3.908      1 Template:Ref\n  1.01%    2.474      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.53%    1.305      1 Template:References\n  0.34%    0.841      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:18573-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403143520 and revision id 323349\n -->\n",
